<section style="padding:72px 24px 40px;"><div style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;"><div class="rich"><p>Ashland sits right between Lincoln and Omaha off I-80, close enough to Mahoney State Park that a lot of families move here for the small-town feel and stay for the commute. That growth has brought new developments on the edges of town, but it sits alongside an older historic core with homes that have been standing for generations. Both types of houses tend to have the same basement problem: windows too small to serve as a legal fire exit.</p><p>Lincoln Egress Windows works with Ashland homeowners who are converting basements into extra bedrooms for multigenerational living, finishing a lower level for growing kids, or getting a house ready to list. We handle the full job, from the <a href="/egress-window-cost/">estimate</a> through the cut-in and window well installation, so the finished room passes inspection and actually functions as a safe way out.</p></div></div></section>
<section style="padding:0 24px 64px;"><div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;">
    <span class="kicker">What We Do in Ashland</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);margin:0 0 28px;">Services for Ashland Properties</h2>
    <div class="feat-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:20px;">
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Egress Window Installation</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">Full cut-in installation for Ashland basements, sized to meet Nebraska code so the room can legally be called a bedroom. See our <a href="/egress-window-installation-lincoln/">egress window installation</a> process.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Egress Window Replacement</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">Replacing undersized basement windows with properly sized egress units, common in Ashland's older homes near the historic downtown. Details on <a href="/egress-window-replacement-lincoln/">egress window replacement</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Window Well Installation</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">Steel or polyethylene window wells built to handle Nebraska freeze-thaw cycles and drain well after heavy rain, whether your lot is flat or slopes toward the Platte. Learn more about <a href="/window-well-installation-lincoln/">window well installation</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 8px;">Basement Window Replacement</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">Standard basement window swaps for Ashland homeowners who want a more secure, better-sealed window without finishing the space just yet. More on <a href="/basement-window-replacement-lincoln/">basement window replacement</a>.</p>
      </div>
</div>
